Thank you @israel21c for a great article covering our @nuabeverlyhills story and the great @telavivgroove project 🙏🙏
A big project is about to start, but what I like to do most is making food to my love @talnavarro1 #familyfirst❤️ #lovee#mywife #avocadotoasts #breakfastatmyhouse

This is Chef Yoav Schverd from Nua Restaurant in Beverly Hills.
Above all, Yoav is an old friend and especially loved.
Yoav was the first to embrace Orly's idea for the series events of Tel Aviv Groove  in LA and did as much as he could to help the idea become a reality.
We love you Yoav!❤️
@yoavschverd @nuabeverlyhills @orly_segal

And its a wrap!
I had the privilege, together with @gailscatering , to cater, manage and cook at the beautiful 3 days IAC Annual event in Austin.
With an amazing partners and a great team, we overcame any challenge and cooked almost 40 meals, for a total of more than 2,000 people. 
It was exciting, and I’m grateful for @israeliamerican for giving us the opportunity to do it.
And don’t forget - “Everybody needs a @ronniebenarie “

Till next time…

I don’t need Valentine Day to celebrate you.
Love is everyday.
In the little things. 
In real life. 
In actions. 
Grateful for you. For us.
My partner, my balance, my love.
My MAN.
❤️

Culinary embassy is taking a culinary symbol like pita bread with Israeli flavours to a place like the surfers beach in Malibu California.
That what my friends did. @yoavschverd , an old friend, and his partner @ronniebenarie , a new and beloved friend.
The new place name is PITA BU - @thepitabu .
If you are in LA… go grab a pita.
Me and my adorable 🥰 sous chef are making Frittata for breakfast… #familyfirst❤️ #lovemyfamily❤️
Albacore tuna, crispy shallots, melon, watermelon mint jalapeños juice. #gofresh #rawfish #beverlyhillsrestaurants
“Give a hungry man a fish, you feed him for a day” (Lao Tsu). But making my love @talnavarro1 sashimi - she would smile for the whole week❤️ #familyfirst #laotzu #sashimi

(Scroll ↔️) 🩵🩵🩵Happy anniversary to us @yoavschverd 

Life is a magical journey.
And everyone has his own path in this world.

7 years ago we exchange vows in the most magical and beautiful experience, surrounded by nature, amazing people and loads of love and high energies.

We did not know this is only the beginning of a remarkable book with so many chapters, we call “our life”.

Love exploring life with you, my best partner in crime 🤍

To many years more. I love you ❤️

Happy Rose Ha Shanna 🍏 שנה טובה ומתוקה❤️🍯
 שתהיה זו שנה אחרת, שנה של הכלה, של סובלנות, של אהבה וקבלת האחר.
שנה שבה הרוע שבעולם יעלם או לפחות, יפחת.
שכל ילד יקבל את ההזדמנות שלו לגדול במשפחה ובסביבה תומכת, אוהבת, מחבקת ומכילה.
שכל נער ידע להתמודד עם מצבי קיצון בלימודים ובין החברים, שכל ילדה ואשה יוכלו לחיות בשיוויון זכויות, שתהיה פחות אלימות ויותר הקשבה
ושרוב הדאגות יוסרו מלבבות האנשים, כך גם יהיה פחות סיכוי למחלות..

🌟 Reflecting on My Birthday 🌟
Today, as the clock strikes midnight on the 31st, I turn a year older. But this birthday feels different, more profound. 

This year It’s not just about me. 

It’s about rebirth, about lives transforming in the face of adversity.
So many people have reborn.

Many have faced loss and emerged into a life marked by an aching absence. 💔
Newborns have entered a world marred by conflict. 🖤

Survivors of unimaginable horrors have reborn into renewed gratitude in the gift of life. 🌹

This year, I’m not looking to celebrate in the usual way. Instead, I have a birthday wish from all of you. 💝

In the spirit of the new civil year, let’s introspect. 
Ask yourself: 
How can I contribute positively today? 
To others, to the world, to my family? 
How can I bridge divides and foster unity?
Find the answer within you and do it.

Make a change. 

Do good 🩷

I hope this year is full of miracles. We really need them. Let’s hope for safety and back home to our beloved hostages, peace for our soldiers, and an end to hard times. 
I wish for peace for all of us and everyone as soon as possible ☮️ 

Amen 🙏🏼
Happy new year 🎈

In the image: my light in the dark. ❤️My New Year’s resolution 🙏🏼My family ❤️
